\section{Conclusion}

Exercise 1 demonstrated the importance of careful data cleaning. The presence of mixed reporting units and missing attributes (such as the Male category) required specific preprocessing steps. By deriving the male population data and standardising the units, we were able to visualize that while global enrolment trends are similar across genders, a persistent gap remains between male and female education participation.

